Store Outcome Data in the Patient Program Outcome Management Data Model (Pilot)

With Patient Program Outcome Management, you can define program outcomes and indicators, and link program outcomes and patient progress with the ability to measure at the outcomes level. This data is stored in the Patient Program Outcome Management data model.

Where: Enterprise and Unlimited editions with Life Sciences Cloud or Health Cloud license.
When: Available starting in June 2024.
Who: Users with Health Cloud Starter (for Life Sciences Cloud) or Health Cloud Foundation (for Health Cloud), and Patient Program Outcome Management permission set.
